	<entry>
		<title>U10 and U11 Hampton Football Tournament</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="/westward/latest-news/258-u10-and-u11-hampton-football-tournament.html"/>
		<published>2013-10-07T07:12:31Z</published>
		<updated>2013-10-07T07:12:31Z</updated>
		<id>https://westwardschool.co.uk/westward/latest-news/258-u10-and-u11-hampton-football-tournament.html</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mrs Stevenson</name>
		<email>westwardschool@btconnect.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
	&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HAMPTON 5-A-SIDE FOOTBALL TOURNAMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	After the heat on Thursday &lt;span class=&quot;scayt-misspell&quot; data-scayt_word=&quot;5th&quot; data-scaytid=&quot;1&quot;&gt;5th&lt;/span&gt; September, Saturday &lt;span class=&quot;scayt-misspell&quot; data-scayt_word=&quot;7th&quot; data-scaytid=&quot;3&quot;&gt;7th&lt;/span&gt;, the day of the 5-a-side tournament, was totally different. The parents and boys were all hoping the weather would hold for the day as playing in the rain would have been miserable.&lt;/p&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
	&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HAMPTON 5-A-SIDE FOOTBALL TOURNAMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	After the heat on Thursday &lt;span class=&quot;scayt-misspell&quot; data-scayt_word=&quot;5th&quot; data-scaytid=&quot;1&quot;&gt;5th&lt;/span&gt; September, Saturday &lt;span class=&quot;scayt-misspell&quot; data-scayt_word=&quot;7th&quot; data-scaytid=&quot;3&quot;&gt;7th&lt;/span&gt;, the day of the 5-a-side tournament, was totally different. The parents and boys were all hoping the weather would hold for the day as playing in the rain would have been miserable.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
